KR:
&lt;그건 그냥 신경 안 써도 되는 뒷문 변화라고 파우스트가 그랬는데.&gt;
EN:
&lt;But Faust said that that Backdoor volatility wasn't anything for us to worry about.&gt;

KR:
&lt;결국 몰래 화면을 훔쳐 봤다는 거네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;So you took a peep at the screen.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…돈키호테, 설마!&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Don Quixote, you didn't...!&gt;

KR:
&lt;그러게, 히스클리프. 대체 왜 그러는 걸까?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Right, Heathcliff. I just don't understand why some people keep doing things that everyone tells them not to.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래서… 지금 다 같이 불러 모아서 거길 탐험하자는 건가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Are you... suggesting that we call everyone over to explore that place?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…면담이 무서운 건 아니고?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... You're just scared of the 'consultation', aren't you?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…위험해 보이면 바로 돌아오는 거다.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Fine. But we're turning around at the first sign of danger.&gt;

KR:
&lt;사실 너도, 옷을 구할 수 있다면 해볼 만하다고 생각했잖아.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Come on. You were willing to do it if it meant that you could pick up some clothes.&gt;
